Region II. Km 127 on road from San Pedro de Atacama to Paso Jama. At NW end of the Salar del Quisquito. Wet alluvial fan down steep mountainside. Bofedal vegetation along stream course. Common plants in drier areas: Stipa, Lepidophyllum, Festuca. In wet areas: Oxychloe (but not pungent), Deyeuxia and small Eleocharis (rare).
